<doc id="359516" wikidata="Q1137081" url="?curid=359516" title="Countess (band)">
<text>Countess is a black metal band from the Netherlands. Formed in 1992, they have released more than a dozen full-length albums and are considered one of the most eminent Dutch black metal bands. After years of being a solo project, as of 2014, they are a band again and play live.

