<doc id="359529" wikidata="Q1178971" url="?curid=359529" title="FGM (disambiguation)">
<text>FGM stands for female genital mutilation, the removal of some or all of the external female genitalia for non-medical reasons.

FGM may also refer to:

* Fisher&#x27;s geometric model, an evolutionary model
* Flamelet generated manifold, a chemistry reduction technique
* Functionally graded material, in materials science
* Free Gaza Movement

